1.1.name: wordpress/seo-wpbooster
1.1.description:
EN:

Attention please! World wide version (wpbooster.com) of this SEO plugin is still under development and will be released within 3 to 6 months. Now, we have only local, polish version, which description you can find below the english one. WPBooster SEO plugin is designed especially for advertisement and SEO linkbuilding for blog posts of users registered in WPBooster system. Advantages: free links on post with similar content (advanced contextual post matching engine) which will improve positions in search engines, full automatic SEO system, solution type "switch on and forget", full control (you don't have to know SEO, system will automatically set best parameters for your blog, but if you want to do so, there is nice control panel ;)), statistics of distributed advertising links.

PL:

Plugin WPBooster służy do reklamy i pozycjonowania wpisów na blogach użytkowników należących do systemu. Działanie wtyczki polega na w pełni automatyczny
